data.description: This home is a short sale.  Welcome to your new home in the heart of Hanover, Pennsylvania! This stunning, newly constructed townhouse offers modern living at its finest. With 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 2 half baths, a secondary living room in the basement, and a garage, this move-in-ready home is designed for comfort and convenience.  Step inside, and you'll be immediately impressed by the fresh and contemporary design. The open-concept main level is flooded with natural light, creating a bright and inviting space for daily living and entertaining.  The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, sleek countertops, and plenty of storage space. It's the perfect place to whip up delicious meals and create lasting memories with loved ones.  Upstairs on the third level, you'll find three bedrooms, each offering ample closet space and a comfortable atmosphere for rest and relaxation. The primary bedroom boasts a private ensuite bathroom, providing a peaceful retreat at the end of the day.  The basement, complete with a secondary living room, adds valuable living space to the home. Whether you envision a cozy family room, a home office, or a playroom, this area is versatile and ready to accommodate your needs.  With a garage, you'll have secure parking and additional storage space, making daily life more convenient.  This newly built townhouse offers all the advantages of modern construction, including energy efficiency, and updated systems.  Located in Hanover, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and local amenities, as well as the charm of a friendly community.  Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this newly constructed townhouse your own. Schedule your showing today and experience the convenience, comfort, and modern elegance that await you in Hanover, Pennsylvania.
